self.setUpClass()
nqubits = 5
p = ql.Program('a_program', platf, nqubits)
k = ql.Kernel('a_kernel', platf, nqubits)
for i in range(2):
    k.gate('prepz', [i])
for i in range(2):
    k.gate('h', [i])
k.gate('cnot', [0, 1])
k.gate('cz', [0, 1])
p.set_sweep_points([10])
p.add_kernel(k)
p.compile()
